    "agendaChanges": "Section 4 (Reconvene/Roll Call/Report Out on Closed Session) and Section 5 (Welcome) were handled together at the start of the recording, with the president giving the closed session report and then the welcome. Section 6 (Changes to the Agenda) had no changes announced. Sections 1-3 (Closed Session) are not captured in this recording. The meeting proceeded largely in agenda order. Section 9 (School/Community Reports) featured Warren Sater (Adelante Selby principal) speaking briefly before the video. The COVID-19 discussion (12.1) included presentations from Garfield, Roosevelt, and Taft principals (Lupe Torres, Tina Mercer, Anna Herrera) as well as Dr. Baker on the Governor's proposal. Items 12.2, 12.3, and 12.4 (board policy first readings) were presented together by Wendy Kelly. Public comment for item 12.1 was taken mid-discussion. Sections 16, 17, 18, 19, and 20 were handled rapidly at the end.",
